<L>__{exterior berlin park day}
<A>__{roderick and the chevalier walking.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{and i think he was as much affected as i was at thus finding one of his kindred; for he, too, was an exile from home, and a friendly voice, a look, brought the old country back to his memory again, and the old days of his boyhood.}
<C>__{chevalier}
<D>__{i'd give five years of my life to see the old country again, the greenfields, and the river, and the old round tower, and the burying place.}
